In this presidential memorandum, issued on April 12, 2017, the President delegates authority to the Director of the Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) to submit a report required under section 1907(d) of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2017. The memorandum states that any future Public Law containing a provision similar to section 1907(d) of the Act will also fall under the authority of this delegation. The memorandum also instructs the Director of the FBI to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.